animeDescription: Q-taro, a monster, is living with the Ohara family. He can fly and make his body transparent, but he cannot turn his body into other things like other monsters do. He is a scattered mind, and he always makes mistakes and causes trouble.(Source: AnimeNfo)
animeRelated: ['Adaptation: Obake no Q-tarou', 'Sequel: Shin Obake no Q-tarou']
